{"tid":1534953,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一人一信去教育局投訴大埔何中","createTime":"2019-09-03T07:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T01:47:57.000Z","uid":307569,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4b9e45efce464165bd697de1c5a5f074f70cd5","tid":1534953,"uid":307569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:26:31.000Z","msg":"2/9網上流傳一段錄音，懷疑是大埔孔教學院大成何郭佩珍中學校長梁秋雲，向罷課的學生表示，他們沒有「絕對自由」去選擇在那間課室活動，如果學生認為自己要有自由，唯一便是不做這間學校的學生；有學生又問，學校是否會把已被點名的罷課學生名單交予教育局，懷疑是梁秋雲的聲音回應指，教育局有指引要學校上交罷課學生數目，所以校方會交，又指「間間學校都有」。<br />\n<br />\nsdotp3@edb.gov.hk <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDear EDB <br />\n<br />\nI am writing to express my concern over he ruthless behavior of the school principal.    <br />\n<br />\nMs Leung reported the no. of students joined class boycott to the Education Bureau. This white terror spreads at campus. Students are worried if they get punished. Students who boycott classes were locked in the lecture hall. There was a recording that the principal said the students had no right to choose where to gather unless they drop out. She also betrayed the students and called the police to hurt the students. <br />\n<br />\nthe students also said that Ms Leung tried to flee school and refused to talk to them. When they tried to stop her, her car crashed into the crowd. She intended to kill the students!<br />\n<br />\nI am very worried if the students are influenced by the cold-blooded and immoral behavior of the principal who has affects students negatively. <br />\n<br />\nI now demand EDB to explain on whether school is asked to report the figure and submit a list of students who boycott the class.  Pls also investigate the issue and reply us that how you would do to such a cold-blooded principal.  <br />\n<br />\nYours sincerely<br />\nxxx"},{"pid":"1cc1d612b3293a3a4a085fc17644919421f66662","tid":1534953,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:26:44.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><s